      <title>报告显示美国库存增加，油价连续两天下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-09/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-april-10</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在一份行业报告指出美国原油库存增加后，油价连续两天下跌，尽管中东紧张局势不断升温以及欧佩克+持续实施的限制措施预计将限制跌势。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-09/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-april-10</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 09 Apr 2024 23:15:34 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
